Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasaneau setsuna o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitto eien to shinjikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no sora
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari o kou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoudou ga mushibande yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Risei o kakikesu libido
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:00:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochikitta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Minikui sugata ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hito no namida kareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa boku o dou omou no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotae o oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NMakka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna o nurashiai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NYowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Futari wa ikite yuku no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu o nameatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei o teigi shiatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o musabotte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Offline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A complete transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't drink any blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get Tsukasa from-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He dodged me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just tell me that if you transformed,\Nit was my job to keep Tsukasa safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her to me, now! I'm taking her to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me, Anzai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai... it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought... I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shot in the stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet... it's stuck in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this right where the bullet hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Zero Sev... the sniper. She gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to thank-!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He regained his sanity while still transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If he went through the proper training,\Nhe might learn to really control himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it, Zero Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that face... Makimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish all devil-human couples could be like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not hurt that badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your first time shooting a human.\NWasn't that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much different from sniping devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm shooting from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Tsukasa always administer\Nyour sedatives for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a good idea for me to be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Told them there were people with guns\Non the roofs of two hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't say a word about Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me play with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Japanese is so good!\NHuh? A foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this doctor, a friend of Yanagi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that to control the devil inside me,\NI have to get to know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's important to figure out\Nwhat triggers my transformation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and exactly how far it makes me transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I'd never thought about it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to hurt you, so I always thought\Nit would be better to keep my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much every time I transform,\Nit has something to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I want to learn more about why I transform,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to drag you into it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It would mean putting you in more danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ever want to do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I never actually talked to you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at the hotel, it was just like\Nwhen you saved me at the college.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew I was bleeding, but you still ran to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time, I'd been shot.\NI could have been bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy you came for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had lost it and bitten you,\Nwould you still be able to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't end there.\NDevils drink blood, and much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Lee would have stopped you\Nbefore that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you brought him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like insurance, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One or two bites aren't going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But getting bit hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she always this reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical pain doesn't bother me that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much harder not being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was never about her reliability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I guess I'm being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I know this is hard on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She never lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think my face is disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,D-did somebody say it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them bother you!\NThey're just being cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who told me I was disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it will be dangerous for us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to leave you alone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You might run off and get yourself hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That doctor told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ways to train yourself\Nto control your bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But to do it, you'll need her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a little concerned about what it might mean\Nto control the devil inside me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, oh yeah. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Come on, now I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Does... does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we're a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Does this mean we're a couple?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We really haven't talked about any\Nof the important stuff, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. Um, I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you mind if I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The sedative hasn't worn off yet,\Nso I don't think I'll transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai's a bigger perv than he lets on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You better watch yourself, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Emergency Ward Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager of Cross Bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiwako Oe and her employee\NWataru Akase, both dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ryunosuke Katagiri is in hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's virtually immobilized for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people died because of him.\NThat should be warning enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,C Squad, Ushio, private line. Status report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven and Zero Nine appear to have\Nescaped the Mino Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The workers who went up to inspect\Nthe water tank had their uniforms stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and were left tied up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a devil showed up and took her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Six says it was Anzai from F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a tip earlier from what\Nsounded like a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He said there were snipers on top of the Mino Hotel,\Nand the Grand Hotel across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood spatter on the roof will eventually\Ntell them that Makimura was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was nothing in the tip\Nabout you being a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Anzai's just a low-rank officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be that he couldn't make the call on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep an eye on F Squad for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you find out who the hostage was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And, this is just a hunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think Anzai and the hostage are lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the boy has gotten old enough to\Nfall in love with a human, just like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from the hair color,\Nhe and his father are identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, if he gets to be any more like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The half-devil son of a mass murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My interest in you is piqued again, Yuuki Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After I move to the bar,\Nwe'll be able to see each other every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have people in to fix it next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring all of your valuables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is just asking people to come rob it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be seeing this apartment again for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When everything calms down,\NI hope we can relax under the kotatsu again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone fishy's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not with the police. It's an amateur stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be a reporter or a trouble-seeker,\Ntrying to get a look at Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people saw her during the Ikebukuro Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Tsukasa Taira?\NSome people have leaked her name and school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing the subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are rumors going around about\Na new group that's trying to wipe out all devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chosen Civil Community.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So they think they're chosen, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Ikebukuro Incident,\Nit's only to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Groups like this were bound to pop up. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little too soon for a group to be fully formed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see the happy couple's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready for some bloodlust training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anzai Couple will be in Guest Room A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi and I will be standing by\Nin Room B next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a few restraining devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all made with devils in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we supposed to do, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll actually have you transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I thought this training was to help me control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to control it, we need to learn\Nthe timing of your transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And the point of the training is to be able to\Ncontrol the transformation after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Control doesn't mean "stop,"\Nit means gaining mastery over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to stop the bloodlust,\Nall I can tell you is to stop dating women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stress so much.\NThis is why we have these devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock yourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And hey, we'll be watching you live\Nfrom next door in Room B.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we only needed a doctor\Nto watch if we were doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, it's only to make communication\Neasier between Rooms A and B.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have it off most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, depending on how things go,\Nyou might end up wanting to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Yanagi and I will be monitoring\Nyour temperature from Room B.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you transform and your temperature rises\Nabove the control value...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we will force the audio channel open\Nand address you from the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will then ask, "Are you hurt?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You must both answer this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we feel it necessary,\Nwe will also turn on the video feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-they really are keeping this offline, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's not, then that doctor has some\Nserious problems he needs to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Maybe this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The microphone and the camera are both X-ed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it should be okay th-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you put these on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nail protectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They protect your nails when they've grown,\Nand measure the added length.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these handcuffs? They're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should take them off.\NI feel kind of weird about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I like it. I feel like it's safer this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!\NThat's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I just hit you where you got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already healed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The skin feels kind of tight, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! I didn't even think. I just reached out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you can touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That was a weird yelp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna touch...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His pulse went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And his temp went up one degree centigrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry. Did you not like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mind. It's okay. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the control value?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,34 degrees centigrade,\Nthe average transformation temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Four degrees to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take my bra off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Three degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,R-relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch me... lower...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your temperature is above the control value.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,N...no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he didn't hear him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't answer soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the video...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning the video feed on, just in case.\NYou have one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for not stopping sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did he hear the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've settled down, I'll start asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That little yelp when I touched Anzai's nipple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When I pushed her down and we were\Nin that position and I pressed against her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A small sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She was really turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to touch her. I want to be in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:16:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to lick her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want... to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a good idea to assign a new leader\Nto Public Security Division 5's F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a habit of allowing his subordinates\Nto disobey orders when told to stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,F Squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Sawazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We had trouble with him before,\Nwith him and a devil inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The skies are clear. The weather report was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to Tokyo since\Nmy high school class trip, Chief Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. We're not here for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want you to call me by my\Nmaiden name while we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we get back to Obihiro, it's "Chief Sako."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Redeyes' Rights Protection Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,R2PC for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a civil rights committee that works to\Npreserve human rights for devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I happen to be on that committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The main reason I'm in Tokyo to begin with\Nis to attend this conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it makes sense, but Tsukasa, too?\NIs there some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you must be tired from training,\Nand thought I'd give you a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My signature can get up to two of my guests\Nfree dinner at the hotel restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How is ONLO doing these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. It's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear more of your high school kids\Nare looking to be police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And how are things at the lab, might I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you promised not to pry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you might run into\Na handsome stranger later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The fellow who gave me a ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The view here is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We are on the 46th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant's one floor down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it opens at six, so you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Let me stop by the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it official, but what does it even really mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep up with the training...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will it come more naturally?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You looked like someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Ecological Research\N{\an5}Department Director\N{\an5}Midori Sako
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to the conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not on the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a friend's chauffeur tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye. Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You be good to her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've never seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She kind of reminds me of you, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I might run into a handsome stranger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That old bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki has grown into a handsome young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you could have seen him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point in time,\Nwe should hold off on passing the law
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing devil-human sex with a doctor present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ONLO is working to develop restraining devices\Nto use during intercourse,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are issues that need to be resolved first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the safety of these devices\Nand availability to the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing the new law without\Naddressing these issues
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,would be like setting a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the Ikebukuro Incident has made\Nthe devils' existence public knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Susumu Sofue\N{\an5}Minister\N{\an4}Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare\N{\an5}Kaname Shirase\N{\an5}Parliamentary Secretary\N{\an5}Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think that the government\Nmight be using this new law
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to capture devils and\Neliminate them from our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto tokete yuku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Motto ai shiaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nani o tsutaerareta no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o tsumugenai meguriawase
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare ka yurushite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kegareta sugata ga boku de aru koto o
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fureru yubi ga furueteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:22:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu tsukezu ni mamoritai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anata dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of desire forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aragai tsuzukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakiagaru shoudou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aa, mata boku wa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto futari tokete yuku you ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Obihiro National Laboratory\N{\an5}Bionomic Research Facility
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so sudden, I couldn't just come out\Nand say, "Hi, I'm your mother."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But, oh, how he's grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He even has a human girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm a little worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:23:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also had a feeling that they would be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw both of their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to tell you so badly,\NI came back as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But there weren't any direct flights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could hug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Or Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the day comes that you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Command."
